OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly clear
OL,6,Fand dry to begin with, but some cloud
OL,7,Fmoving into Cornwall through the
OL,8,Fevening, spreading to Devon later. A
OL,9,Fcooler night for some, but feeling
OL,10,Fmuggy in places, mostly in the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FCloud in Cornwall will lift
OL,13,Fthrough the morning leaving another
OL,14,Fbright and hot day. Cooler for
OL,15,FCornwall but hotter further towards
OL,16,Fthe east.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
